{
  "texts": [
    "A screenshot of the scoring interface on the itemlevel can be found in Figure 10 in Appendix A.4.",
    "For preliminary testing of our scoring implementation, we manually scored 22 EITs taken with our system.",
    "Scoring each item on a scale of 0-4, we followed the established scoring scheme of Ortega et al. (2002), with the sum of all item scores as the total EIT score.",
    "The EITs consisted of 24 items, resulting in a maximum total score of 96 for the manual scoring.",
    "We then correlated the total manual EIT scores with the total automatic scores of these 22 tests in ILAP."
  ]
}